{"tid":1238683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講呢五位係上星期既暴徒","createTime":"2019-06-18T02:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T07:54:10.000Z","uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7ead4b72a04297cb20809b933dbf51d40aa03cc3","tid":1238683,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i8.bangqu.com/r2/news/20180228/30495179735150383173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi8.bangqu.com%2Fr2%2Fnews%2F20180228%2F30495179735150383173.jpg&h=268ceb50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢五個後生仔真係暴徒黎，響度亂我香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地見到既暴徒係咪佢地？"},{"pid":"681c8207aaebde0edfd98366315191c995a7554e","tid":1238683,"uid":2267,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"有記者已經影到五位暴徒真身<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiOiHvV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiOiHvV.png&h=773d9b6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20677a6120e1a4beac57736f378a2ab5fd179138","tid":1238683,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:05:31.000Z","msg":"呢五件自爆撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd4795c2549c88818796da80ea0ac8018bfd479","tid":1238683,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f94c96b35fa475cab0a0ae8b72a98e1b7cd47c1b","tid":1238683,"uid":261530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:10:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bcb2cb7c4bec6610b6bac9db2d9573832ec292e","tid":1238683,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f94c96b35fa475cab0a0ae8b72a98e1b7cd47c1b","tid":1238683,"uid":261530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"681c8207aaebde0edfd98366315191c995a7554e","tid":1238683,"uid":2267,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"有記者已經影到五位暴徒真身<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiOiHvV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiOiHvV.png&h=773d9b6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:10:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a8a8ea314f5d4a980fa55e0cdfbf072674a173","tid":1238683,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"1. 仍然有5個人被控暴動罪，即係暴動的定性無變過。<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察想分化示威者，等你地以為得5個人好少就割席。<br />\n<br />\n3. 好多人用「得5個人暴動就要用咁多催淚彈」依件事嚟講笑，話嗰5個人係咪Avengers。你地已經中咗警察奸計。<br />\n而家有5個人被控暴動罪，唔等於最後只有依5個人被控暴動罪。<br />\n最終被控暴動罪的人一定唔只5個，警察睇完錄影就會搵到多啲人告。<br />\n<br />\n4. 根據《公安條例》第245章第19條：「如任何參與憑藉第18(1)條被定為非法集結的集結的人破壞社會安寧，該集結即屬暴動，而集結的人即屬集結暴動。」<br />\n即係一旦有人被控告暴動罪入咗，其他和平的人都算係參與咗暴動，只係暫時無比人告。<br />\n一日612仍然被定性為「暴動」，當日出現喺現場的人都有機會被控暴動罪（不論是否和平）。"},{"pid":"153a404a43986a70024a30536e76f392f6e312ae","tid":1238683,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"都幾尷尬 不如收手"},{"pid":"910ba9c163006b8615ca9f4f56441c4c68ad3908","tid":1238683,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd4795c2549c88818796da80ea0ac8018bfd479","tid":1238683,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:47:15.000Z","msg":"無gear就咁撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e098a74058d7ca0d0ffbf2e07a0ee44be17d926d","tid":1238683,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"681c8207aaebde0edfd98366315191c995a7554e","tid":1238683,"uid":2267,"like":47,"dislike":0,"s